+Phase 3C goal
+
+Turn this:
+
+tick → diff → events → consequences
+
+into this:
+
+tick → diff → events → consequences → active effects → next tick influence
+
+So the world gains momentum, not just state changes.
+
+What Phase 3C adds
+Backend
+active effects stored in simulation state
+consequence → effect mapping
+effect decay / expiry
+effect influence on next tick
+effect diff + summary
+deterministic application order
+Frontend
+show active effects in simulation tab
+show new/expired effects in diff panel
+include effects in history summaries
+Rules for Phase 3C
+Must stay deterministic
+
+No randomness.
+
+Must stay bounded
+
+Cap active effects and decay them.
+
+Must stay inspectable
+
+Every effect should have:
+
+source consequence
+target entity
+duration
+magnitude
+type
+New simulation state fields
+
+Store in metadata.simulation_state:
+
+{
+  "tick": 3,
+  "threads": {...},
+  "factions": {...},
+  "locations": {...},
+  "history": [...],
+  "events": [...],
+  "consequences": [...],
+  "active_effects": [
+    {
+      "effect_id": "eff_thr_market_pressure",
+      "type": "pressure_boost",
+      "target_type": "thread",
+      "target_id": "thr_market",
+      "magnitude": 1,
+      "duration": 2,
+      "source_consequence_id": "cnsq_thr_market_pressure"
+    }
+  ],
+  "step_hash": "ab12cd34"
+}
+Effect types for Phase 3C
+
+Start with a small set:
+
+Thread effects
+pressure_boost
+pressure_dampen
+Faction effects
+faction_strain_boost
+faction_relief
+Location effects
+heat_boost
+heat_dampen
+Generic
+hotspot_seed
+incident_risk
+
+Keep it small for now.
+
+Deterministic effect mapping
+Consequence → effect
+Consequence type	Effect
+pressure_increase	pressure_boost on thread
+faction_response	faction_strain_boost on faction
+hotspot	heat_boost on location
+
+Magnitude:
+
+default 1
+
+Duration:
+
+default 2
+hotspot effects can use 3
+New backend module
+
+Create:
+
+src/app/rpg/creator/world_effects.py
+
+This module owns:
+
+effect creation
+effect application
+decay
+cleanup
